# Program Roadmap Governance

- Operate in fixed 12-week cycles with explicit plan, build, harden, and closeout checkpoints.
- At cycle start, define scope tied to one annual thesis capability objective.
- At cycle close, require an evidence pack with:
  - scenario metadata and seeds,
  - metric pass/fail outputs,
  - baseline deltas,
  - ADR IDs updated in the cycle.
- Do not mark cycle success unless both dual objectives are satisfied:
  - scientific-grade fidelity and determinism,
  - high real-time runtime performance.
- If evidence is incomplete, treat cycle as incomplete rather than done.
